commit.message: Add history and bump version for 0.3.0
Add tox and Travis CI config

Add tests for multipart decoder matcher

- Add tests too

Implement equality for multipart/form-data

This could have a few problems:

1. The ordering of the parts might be different causing this to return
   False when in fact the requests are *semantically* equivalent

2. If there's any dynamic content in a part's content, it will be return
   False as well.

Start working on a multipart/form-data matcher

See: https://github.com/sigmavirus24/betamax/issues/64
Fix bug found while feeding the dog
Add first matcher and a couple tests
Add dev-requirements for contributors and Travis
